title: Alec Baldwin suggests Trump is the 'virus in the US': 'Vaccine arrives in November'
description: Alec Baldwin on Tuesday suggested that President Trump is the "virus" in the United States, alluding to the coronavirus that has sickened and killed thousands worldwide.
